ong></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">情绪不稳定、经常焦虑、过于放大一点点沮丧程度、需要别人来安抚自己。</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: center; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">★ 驱动型父母</strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></strong></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">总是追求完美、目标性强且忙碌、缺乏同情心、试图控制孩子的生活。</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: center; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">★ 消极型父母</strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></strong></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">逃避处理过于棘手问题、无法成为孩子的依靠。<span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">对孩子受伤等视而不见，并让孩子去解决问题。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">★ 拒绝型父母</strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></strong></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">不喜欢情感亲密、不愿意被孩子打扰、很少参与到家庭生活、多数只想做自己的事情。</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 20px 0% 15px; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); -webkit-transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); -moz-transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); -o-transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); text-align: right; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(8, 59, 129); display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; line-height: 1.3; padding: 0px 0.2em; background-color: rgb(8, 59, 129); font-size: 22px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">评</strong></p></section><section style="display: inline-block; padding: 0px 0.5em; color: rgb(8, 59, 129); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">点</p></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px; background-position: 25.8037% -43.1473%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: 29.7866%; background-attachment: scroll; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/apprToXjJCE2967/image/ueditor/89385300_1521166799.png&#39;); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">本书不是让我们责怪他人，而是帮助我们更深层次地了解自己，并学习自我治愈。</p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><sectio