atic; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; width: 100%; overflow: hidden !important; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/apprToXjJCE2967/image/ueditor/30773000_1521166800.jpg" style="vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; width: 61.8%; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(103, 102, 102); line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box;">琳赛·吉布森</span></strong></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;">心理学博士</span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;">美国资深临床心理学家</span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;">20多年来专门研究和解决不成熟父母问题</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 20px 0% 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px; background-position: 25.8037% -43.1473%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: 29.7866%; background-attachment: scroll; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/apprToXjJCE2967/image/ueditor/89385300_1521166799.png&#39;); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0% 20px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 5%; overflow: hidden !important; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/apprToXjJCE2967/image/ueditor/37147500_1521166800.png" style="vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 2px; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(67, 90, 152); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">辨认四类不成熟的父母</strong></p></section><section style="max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; vertical-align: bottom; width: 5%; overflow: hidden !important; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/apprToXjJCE2967/image/ueditor/41410300_1521166800.png" style="vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">★ 情绪型父母</strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></strong></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">情绪不稳定、经常焦虑、过于放大一点点沮丧程度、需要别人来安抚自己。</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: center; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">★ 驱动型父母</strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></strong></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">总是追求完美、目标性强且忙碌、缺乏同情心、试图控制孩子的生活。</p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: center; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">★ 消极型父母</strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></strong></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">逃避处理过于棘手问题、无法成为孩子的依靠。<span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">对孩子受伤等视而不见，并让孩子去解决问题。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">★ 拒绝型父母</strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></strong></p><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">不喜欢情感亲密、不愿意被孩子打扰、很少参与到家庭生活、多数只想做自己的事情。</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 20px 0% 15px; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); -webkit-transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); -moz-transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); -o-transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); text-align: right; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(8, 59, 129); display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; line-height: 1.3; padding: 0px 0.2em; background-color: rgb(8, 59, 129); font-size: 22px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">评</strong></p></section><section style="display: inline-block; padding: 0px 0.5em; color: rgb(8, 59, 129); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">点</p></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px; background-position: 25.8037% -43.1473%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: 29.7866%; background-attachment: scroll; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/apprToXjJCE2967/image/ueditor/89385300_1521166799.png&#39;); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">本书不是让我们责怪他人，而是帮助我们更深层次地了解自己，并学习自我治愈。</p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: right; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">——亚瑟·雷曼·弗里曼，心理学博士</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px; background-position: 25.8037% -43.1473%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: 29.7866%; background-attachment: scroll; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/apprToXjJCE2967/image/ueditor/89385300_1521166799.png&#39;); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">帮助从这样家庭中长大的孩子识别情感不健康的父母，了解自己所受的影响，并最终能改善负面的影响，与情感成熟的人建立健康的亲密关系。</p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">—— 泛心理学社区　KnowYourself</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px; background-position: 25.8037% -43.1473%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: 29.7866%; background-attachment: scroll; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/apprToXjJCE2967/image/ueditor/89385300_1521166799.png&#39;); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">本书详细描述了不成熟的父母，被这类父母抚养的孩子的经历、体会，以及解决由此产生的问题的方法。</p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">——尼尔·沃特森博士，临床心理学家</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px; background-position: 25.8037% -43.1473%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: 29.7866%; background-attachment: scroll; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/apprToXjJCE2967/image/ueditor/89385300_1521166799.png&#39;); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">书中的方法操作性强，使你能以更客观的方式觉察他人的行为，改变自我挫败的习惯，并能识别真正能与你保持情感亲密的人，从而摆脱他人的情感操纵，成熟起来。</p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">一一 北京晚报读书编辑　李峥嵘</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 20px 0% 15px; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(8, 59, 129); display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; line-height: 1.3; padding: 0px 0.2em; background-color: rgb(8, 59, 129); font-size: 22px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">目录</p></section><section style="display: inline-block; padding: 0px 0.5em; color: rgb(8, 59, 129); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">精选</p></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0% 20px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 